post:
we have released Proxmox WHMCS module version 1.3.5 with Great New Features that customers were waiting for:

**• Provisioning:** LXC support.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• Product Addons :** Sell IP addon.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• Product Addons :** Sell Max Backups addon.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• KVM Templates:** Multiple IP Pools for KVM DHCP configuration support.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• All Templates:** CPU/RAM/SWAP Resources support for using Fixed as a base line and configoption added on top.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• All Templates:** Product select to show product groups, to help distinguish between products groups with same product names.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• Auto Provisioning:** Compress ipv6 in manual ip assign and ip list like range does.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• Manual Provisioning LXC/Openvz:** Allow reinstall to inherit allowed storage for templates from Auto provisioning Templates for this server.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• Product Setup:** Ability to disable VNC in product setup console dropdown.&lt;br \/&gt;
**• IP Pools:** Support for gateway and subnet input for kvm and lxc.&lt;br \/&gt;

[Change Log](https://modulesfactory.com/changelog.html) | [Read more and Order](https://modulesfactory.com)

Thanks,&lt;br \/&gt;
